data.text:
Asya Satti is a singer who auditioned for Series 6 of Britain's Got Talent. She was twenty five years old at the time of her audition. She hailed from Sweden, however was of Sudanese heritage.

In her audition, Satti sang a song that was never disclosed. Alesha remarked 'The audition has just got a little bit painful'. She was depicted as having been sent home during the audition stage of the competition, however in reality she advanced onto the following round, however she failed to reach the Semi-Finals.

After BGT[]

In 2023, Satti released her debut single entitled 'Look At You Now'.[1]
